{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}
    Bogdan Rusca - Personal Blog
{% endblock %}

{% block stylesheets %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/RuscaBogdanStyle.css') }}">
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div id="hero-card">
        <div id="hero-portrait-container">
            <img id="hero-portrait-img" src="{{ asset('images/RuscaPhoto.jpeg') }}" alt="Bogdan Rusca">
            <h3 id="hero-portrait-support-text">
                Welcome to My Blog
            </h3>
        </div>
        <div id="hero-description">
            <p>
                Hi, I'm Bogdan Rusca, and this is my personal blog where I share thoughts on technology, 
                personal growth, and daily life experiences.
            </p>

            <p class="text-header"> Topics I Cover: </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Latest trends in technology and software development.</li>
                <li>How to stay productive while working remotely.</li>
                <li>The best books and resources for self-improvement.</li>
                <li>Simple daily habits that lead to long-term success.</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                Writing has always been my way of reflecting on experiences and sharing knowledge. Whether it's 
                about coding, problem-solving, or just simple lessons from life, this blog is my space for expression.
            </p>

            <p class="text-header"> My Recent Thoughts: </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Consistency is more important than motivation.</li>
                <li>Why taking breaks improves your focus and creativity.</li>
                <li>How to balance learning new skills while working full-time.</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                Thanks for stopping by! If you enjoy my content, feel free to connect with me or leave a comment.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
